Package fr.univartois.cril.approximation.util

Class CollectionFactory

java.lang.Object
fr.univartois.cril.approximation.util.CollectionFactory
public final class CollectionFactory extends Object
The CollectionFactory provides factory methods instantiating the collections used in the solver. They are designed to return the most efficient known implementation.

    • adaptsAsIndexedCollection

      public static <E> IndexedCollection<E> adaptsAsIndexedCollection(Collection<E> list)
      Creates an indexed collection view of the given list. The resulting view is an object adapter of the list, so any change to the list will alter the view, and vice-versa.
      Type Parameters:
      E - The type of the elements in the collection.
      Parameters:
      list - The list to adapt.
      Returns:
      The created indexed collection.

      public static <E> IndexedCollection<E> unmodifiableIndexedCollection(IndexedCollection<E> collection)
